FormControl.Name: txtPoolName
FormControl.ToolTip: This setting specifies the pool from which the Transformation Server will process.

FormControl.Name: txtMaxProcessingSlotsNumber
FormControl.ToolTip: This setting specifies the number of CPU-intensive background processes that may run concurrently, excluding the idle background processes. The maximum number of processing slots (default: 0) is determined using the following formula: (int)Math.Round(Environment.ProcessorCount * 1.25)

FormControl.Name: ddActivityOrder
FormControl.ToolTip: This setting specifies the order in which the activities are taken for processing.

FormControl.Name: txtResetActivitiesIntervalMinutes
FormControl.ToolTip: This value determines how often activities are checked for overrun.

FormControl.Name: chkOnlineLearningExecutionEnabled
FormControl.ToolTip: If selected, enables processing of the Online Learning task for this Transformation Server instance.

FormControl.Name: chkEnableSynchronousCalls
FormControl.ToolTip: If selected, enables processing of synchronous "pushed" calls.

Confirmation.Message: Are you sure you want to delete this profile? If any agent is using this profile, when the refresh interval passes, the settings will be reverted to default settings.
